OL,3,CPair who planned sex attacks on
OL,4,Cchildren have prison sentences changed
OL,6,FA man who pleaded guilty to a string
OL,7,Fof child sex offences has had his
OL,8,Fprison sentence increased.
OL,10,FStuart Compoton, who was given a life
OL,11,Fsentence on Monday (28 July), will now
OL,12,Fhave to serve a minimum term of more
OL,13,Fthan eight years before he can apply
OL,14,Ffor parole. He was originally
OL,15,Fsentenced to a minimum term of seven
OL,16,Fyears.
OL,18,FIt is because of a miscalculation in
OL,19,Fthe original sentencing.
