OL,3,CPair who planned sex attacks on
OL,4,Cchildren have prison sentences changed
OL,6,FCompton's partner Tracy Turner has had
OL,7,Fher sentence reduced. She will now
OL,8,Fserve 10 years with two years on
OL,9,Fextended license, a reduction of two
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FBoth Turner and Compton admitted six
OL,13,Fcounts of arranging sex with a child.
OL,15,FCompton also pleaded guilty to six
OL,16,Fcounts of making indecent images, and
OL,17,FTurner, who worked as an operating
OL,18,Ftheatre assistant in Cardiff, admitted
OL,19,Ftwo counts of the same offence.
